Package: mvp
Type: Package
Title: Fast manipulation of multivariate polynomials
Version: 1.0-0
Date: 2017-05-18
Author: Robin K. S. Hankin
Depends: mpoly,spray,methods
Suggests: knitr,rmarkdown
VignetteBuilder: knitr
Maintainer: Robin K. S. Hankin <hankin.robin@gmail.com>
Description: Fast manipulation of sparse multivariate polynomials
  using the "Map" class of the Standard Template Library.  The package
  uses the "mpoly" print and coercion methods.  It is comparable in
  speed to the "spray" package, but retains the symbolic aproach of "mpoly".
License: GPL (>= 2)
Imports: Rcpp (>= 0.12.3)
LinkingTo: Rcpp
SystemRequirements: C++11
URL: https://github.com/RobinHankin/mvp.git
BugReports: https://github.com/RobinHankin/mvp/issues
